The zzso Mortality Index zzso is an electronic data file providing all information found on death certificates of former zzso citizens who have died after December zzso zzso zzso follows the example of the National Death Index zzso in the zzso which has provided information on the vital status of US citizens and cause of death since zzso The zzso Mortality Index has been linked successfully to the zzso Cancer Registry and has improved the efficiency of following up cancer zzso A substantial number of death certificates may be checked automatically for the presence of a cancer diagnosis or any other zzso The zzso Mortality Index may be used as a primary source for data on particular causes of zzso It will be used for developing a German zzso for automated coding of medical entities and for determining causes of zzso 
